statements: SELECT * FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'United States' LIMIT 5;
SELECT city, property_type FROM property_listings WHERE price > 100000;
SELECT id, country, city, property_type, price, bedrooms, bathrooms FROM property_listings WHERE bedrooms >= 3 AND bathrooms >= 2;
SELECT * FROM property_listings WHERE price BETWEEN 50000 AND 100000 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT city, property_type, price FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'Canada' AND property_type = 'Condo' ORDER BY price ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'USA' AND price >= 100000 ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT city, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM property_listings GROUP BY city HAVING AVG(price) > 50000;
SELECT property_type, COUNT(id) AS listings_count FROM property_listings GROUP BY property_type ORDER BY listings_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_listings WHERE bedrooms = 3 AND bathrooms = 2 AND price BETWEEN 200000 AND 300000;
SELECT city, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'Canada' GROUP BY city ORDER BY avg_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_listings ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT property_name, price, bedrooms, bathrooms FROM property_listings WHERE price < 100000;
SELECT property_id, property_name, city, area_sqft FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'USA';
SELECT * FROM property_images ORDER BY image_id DESC;
SELECT property_name, price, city FROM property_listings WHERE price BETWEEN 50000 AND 200000;
SELECT property_id, property_name, country, city, price FROM property_listings WHERE bedrooms > 3 ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT * FROM property_listings INNER JOIN property_images ON property_listings.property_id = property_images.property_id WHERE property_listings.city = 'New York' AND property_images.caption LIKE '%kitchen%' ORDER BY property_listings.price ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT property_id, property_name, area_sqft FROM property_listings WHERE country = 'USA' AND city = 'Los Angeles' ORDER BY area_sqft DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT property_id, property_name, city, price FROM property_listings WHERE price BETWEEN 500000 AND 1000000 ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT property_id, property_name, bedrooms, bathrooms FROM property_listings WHERE bedrooms >= 2 AND bathrooms >= 2 ORDER BY property_id ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT city, bedrooms, bathrooms FROM PropertyListing WHERE country = 'USA';

SELECT PropertyListing.city, PropertyListing.price, PropertyReview.rating, PropertyReview.review FROM PropertyListing JOIN PropertyReview ON PropertyListing.id = PropertyReview.listing_id WHERE PropertyListing.price BETWEEN 50000 AND 200000 AND PropertyReview.rating >= 4;
SELECT * FROM Properties LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, country, city, price FROM Properties WHERE bedrooms = 3;
SELECT city, address FROM Properties WHERE country = 'USA' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price FROM Properties;
SELECT id, url FROM Photos JOIN Properties ON Photos.property_id = Properties.id;
SELECT * FROM Properties;
SELECT city, country, price FROM Properties WHERE price > 100000 AND bedrooms >= 3;
SELECT id, city, bathrooms FROM Properties WHERE city = 'New York' OR city = 'London';
SELECT p.id, p.address, c.name AS country FROM Properties p JOIN Countries c ON p.country = c.id;
SELECT p.id, p.price, COUNT(a.id) AS num_amenities FROM Properties p LEFT JOIN Amenities a ON p.id = a.property_id GROUP BY p.id HAVING COUNT(a.id) >= 3;
SELECT * FROM properties;
SELECT title, price FROM properties WHERE id = 1;
SELECT description FROM properties WHERE price < 1000;
SELECT location FROM properties WHERE title LIKE 'Luxury%';
SELECT * FROM countries WHERE country_code = 'US';
SELECT * FROM properties;
SELECT id, title, price FROM properties WHERE price > 1000 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT p.title, p.description, pi.image_url FROM properties p JOIN property_images pi ON p.id = pi.property_id;
SELECT c.country_name, COUNT(p.id) AS property_count FROM countries c LEFT JOIN properties p ON c.country_code = SUBSTR(p.location, 1, 2) GROUP BY c.country_name;
SELECT p.title, a.amenity_name FROM properties p JOIN property_amenities pa ON p.id = pa.property_id JOIN amenities a ON pa.amenity_id = a.amenity_id;
